# Overview

The scripts are designed to deploy services to AWS

## Deploying the dummy service

* At a minimum add the following to your environment variables:

AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=AKIXXXSKSXECDXXXXX
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=pU7jAXXXG/vIyWXXXXXXLBP2h18V/FIDwsmsZuM
FINTEKKERS_CLUSTER_NAME="fintekkers"

* Run python scripts in src/fintekkers/devops in alphabetical order
  * a_check*py
  * b_build_docker*py
  * c_create_ecs_service*py

This will create an ECS service fronted by a load balancer, with the dummy service running on 2 tasks. If you kill a task the ECS cluster will spin up a new one. The load balancer will react accordingly. 
